 Kono ryouri ni shimasu.

81
00:06:15,028 --> 00:06:16,628
 I'll have this dish.

82
00:06:18,388 --> 00:06:23,688
 Sometimes on a menu, the name of the dish is very difficult to pronounce,

83
00:06:24,388 --> 00:06:26,248
 even for native speakers like me.

84
00:06:26,988 --> 00:06:29,688
