 I'm so excited to try that dish.

88
00:06:42,368 --> 00:06:44,388
 To say tanoshimi, there are three phrases.

89
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:49,920
 I'm looking forward to, I'm so excited to, or I can't wait to.

90
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:51,380
 All are fine.

91
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:54,100
 しかし、ものすごく楽しみ。

92
